            "notes": "This deck aims to generate a large number of tokens and sacrifice them for value, dealing damage to opponents in the process. It utilizes cards like Prossh, Skyraider of Kher and Goblin Bombardment to create a loop of sacrificing creatures for damage. Additionally, the deck includes various ramp spells like Farseek and Nature's Lore to quickly build up its resources. Cards like Purphoros, God of the Forge and Impact Tremors provide additional damage as tokens enter the battlefield. The deck also features disruption and removal spells like Thoughtseize and Fatal Push to control the board and protect its combo pieces. Overall, the strategy revolves around generating tokens, sacrificing them for value, and dealing damage to opponents."
